    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Before you begin...</strong></p><p>Get all your ingredients and equipment ready</p><p>Skim through these steps, then wash your fruit and veg</p><p>Note: Equipment and pan sizes vary. Make sure you cook food thoroughly (even if it takes you a little longer than 10 min)</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/ready-to-heat-butter-chicken-curry-with-rice-buttered-spinach-and-naan/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Now lets get started...</strong></p><p>Remove the sleeve from your <strong>butter chicken curry</strong> and pierce the film</p><p>Add the curry to the <strong>microwave</strong> and cook for 5 min or until piping hot, stirring half way</p><p>Tip: Cook for 3 or more? Do this in batches!</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/ready-to-heat-butter-chicken-curry-with-rice-buttered-spinach-and-naan/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil a kettle</p><p>Combine your <strong>garam masala </strong>with a large knob of <strong>butter </strong>in a bowl and mix until fully combined \u2013 this is your <strong>garam masala butter</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/ready-to-heat-butter-chicken-curry-with-rice-buttered-spinach-and-naan/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong> then add to a colander and pour <strong>boiled water</strong> all over it so that it starts to wilt</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/ready-to-heat-butter-chicken-curry-with-rice-buttered-spinach-and-naan/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>wilted spinach</strong> to the bowl with the <strong>garam masala butter </strong>and give everything a good mix up \u2013 this is your <strong>buttered spinach</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/ready-to-heat-butter-chicken-curry-with-rice-buttered-spinach-and-naan/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Squeeze your pouch[es] of <strong>cooked white long grain rice</strong> to separate the grains</p><p>Tear the top corner of the pouch[es] (just a little!) and <strong>microwave</strong> for 2 min or until piping hot</p><p>Tip: If you're cooking two or more pouches, pop them in together but increase the microwave cook time accordingly</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/ready-to-heat-butter-chicken-curry-with-rice-buttered-spinach-and-naan/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>garlic & coriander naan[s]</strong> to a <strong>toaster</strong> for 1-2 min or until warmed through</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/ready-to-heat-butter-chicken-curry-with-rice-buttered-spinach-and-naan/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>butter chicken curry </strong>with the <strong>cooked rice</strong>, <strong>buttered spinach </strong>and <strong>warmed naan </strong>to the side</p><p>Dig in!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
